          <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-amber-500 mb-2">24/7</div>
          <div class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Dedicated Support</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Your account manager available around the clock</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">Corporate Account Benefits</h3>
      
      <div class="space-y-6 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-500 p-6">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-900 mb-2">üìä Centralized Billing & Reporting</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
            Eliminate individual expense reports and reimbursements. Receive one comprehensive monthly invoice with detailed breakdowns by department, cost center, or employee.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1 ml-4">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Customizable billing cycles</li>
