          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1 ml-4">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Tiered pricing structure</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Negotiated contract rates</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ No hidden fees or surcharges</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Transparent, predictable pricing</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-500 p-6">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-900 mb-2">üîó Technology Integration</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
            Seamless integration with your existing systems for booking, approvals, and expense management.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1 ml-4">
            <li>‚Ä¢ API integration available</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Corporate calendar sync</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Multi-user booking portal</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Real-time trip tracking</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

