          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 mt-16">How It Works</h3>
      
      <div class="space-y-6 mb-12">
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-amber-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-2xl">1</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 mb-2">Initial Consultation</h4>
