        </div>
        
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-amber-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-2xl">2</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 mb-2">Custom Proposal</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Receive a tailored proposal with volume-based pricing, service levels, and contract terms designed for your organization.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-amber-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-2xl">3</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 mb-2">Account Setup</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Quick onboarding process including user portal setup, billing configuration, and any system integrations.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-amber-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-2xl">4</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 mb-2">Launch & Support</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Your dedicated account manager ensures smooth service delivery and is available for any questions or special requests.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
