          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Standard terms are Net 30, but we can accommodate other arrangements based on your company's requirements. We accept ACH, credit card, and check payments.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
